===Etymology===
# From Middle English ''[[compounen]]'' < {{MF.}} ''[[comonre]], [[compondre]]'' "to put together"
< {{L.}} ''[[componere]]'' < {{L.}} ''[[com-]]'' "together" + ''[[ponere]]'' "to put".
# Possibly from Malay ''[[kampong]], [[kampung]]'' "group of buildings, village".
[[Category:Malay derivations]]

